('Coleman Propane Fuel Cylinder – 16.4 oz', 'Coleman Propane Fuel Cylinder – 16.4 oz', 'Coleman Propane Fuel Cylinder – 16.4 oz', '基于原文评测：Fuel for your stove—need we say more? Actually, yes, we do have more to say', 'Fuel for your stove—need we say more? Actually, yes, we do have more to say. Make sure you keep an eye out of how much propane you have left, so you don’t roll up to your campsite hangry and tired only to realize you can’t use your stove. Also, be sure to responsibly dispose of e', '{}', '{}'),
('Aeropress Coffee Maker', 'Aeropress Coffee Maker', 'Aeropress Coffee Maker', '基于原文评测：There are several ways to make coffee on the road, but we’re partial to an AeroPress', 'There are several ways to make coffee on the road, but we’re partial to an AeroPress. Sure, it’s not the easiest option out there, but it makes such exceptional coffee that we think the trade-off is worth it. And, yeah, it may not be as easy as a pour over, but it’s also not rock', '{}', '{}'),
('Sterilite 6qt Clear Storage Box White Lid (x2)', 'Sterilite 6qt Clear Storage Box White Lid （2）', 'Sterilite 6qt Clear Storage Box White Lid (x2)', '基于原文评测：These plastic bins are a great, affordable option to organize your cooking supplies', 'These plastic bins are a great, affordable option to organize your cooking supplies. You can easily grab them from the backseat of your car and set them on a picnic table whenever you’re ready to fire up the stove. Use one for traditional supplies—think chef’s knife, bowl, spork,', '{2件装}', '{2-pack}'),
('Sterilite 32qt Clear View Storage Bin with Latch', 'Sterilite 32qt Clear View Storage Bin with Latch', 'Sterilite 32qt Clear View Storage Bin with Latch', '基于原文评测：This flat storage bin easily slides into backseats and trunks, so it’s a good place to keep all of your non-pe', 'This flat storage bin easily slides into backseats and trunks, so it’s a good place to keep all of your non-perishable food (cans of beans, boxes of pasta, etc). Plus, it’s clear, so you can see what food you have and how much you have left at a glance.', '{}', '{}'),
('Reliance Aqua-Tainer – 7 Gal.', 'Reliance Aqua-Tainer – 7 Gal.', 'Reliance Aqua-Tainer – 7 Gal.', '基于原文评测：Not only do you need water for drinking, but it’s necessary for cooking and cleaning up too', 'Not only do you need water for drinking, but it’s necessary for cooking and cleaning up too. We like this container because its shape is designed for easy pouring, the spigot makes doing dishes easy (well, easier), and 7L is a great size.', '{7L容量,速干}', '{7L,quick-dry}'),
