('The North Face Eco Trail Bed 35', 'The North Face Eco Trail Bed 35', 'The North Face Eco Trail Bed 35', '基于原文评测：There’s a variety of highly technical, specialized, expensive sleeping bags on the market', 'There’s a variety of highly technical, specialized, expensive sleeping bags on the market. This one is not one of them—but it’s all you (likely) need for basic car camping. It’s rated to 35℉, which is pretty dang cold, especially since most road trips take place in warm weather m', '{}', '{}'),
