('Hydro Flask 18 oz Standard Mouth Water Bottle', 'Hydro Flask 18 oz Standard Mouth 水瓶', 'Hydro Flask 18 oz Standard Mouth Water Bottle', '基于原文评测：Road tripping with a reusable water bottle is the way to go (beyond environmentalism, who wants to drink lukew', 'Road tripping with a reusable water bottle is the way to go (beyond environmentalism, who wants to drink lukewarm or, even, hot water from a plastic disposable bottle that’s been sitting in the car all day?). This bottle has double wall vacuum insulation to keep cold drinks cold ', '{速干}', '{quick-dry}'),
